Tree

          6
        /   \
       2     8
      / \   / \
     0   4 7   9
        / \
       3   5

p = 2

q = 8

Current Root = 6

2 < 6

8 > 6

They lie on different sides.

Therefore,

6

is the LCA.

Return:

6

